OL,5,Cmaternity law
OL,7,FPeople with disabilities could be
OL,8,Fhelped back into work with similar
OL,9,Fprotections as those for women
OL,10,Freturning from maternity leave, a new
OL,11,Freport has suggested.
OL,13,FA new right to reintegration for
OL,14,Fworkers on sick leave could see firms
OL,15,Fprevented from dismissing someone
OL,16,Funless it is shown the employer has
OL,17,Fmade sufficient efforts at
OL,18,Freintegrating the person, the
OL,19,FResolution Foundation think tank said.
