OL,3,CDisabled could be helped back into
OL,4,Cwork with new right similar to
OL,5,Cmaternity law
OL,7,FThey said such a right would "would
OL,8,Fclarify and strengthen existing legal
OL,9,Fprotections" under the the Equality
OL,10,FAct and "provide a much stronger
OL,11,Fmessage to workers about what they are
OL,12,Fentitled to".
OL,14,FThe report warned that the Government
OL,15,Frisks failing to meet its aim to raise
OL,16,Fthe employment rate to 80% without a
OL,17,F"serious strategy to shift employer
OL,18,Fbehaviour" and argues employers must
OL,19,Fbe incentivised to reintegrate
OL,20,Fexisting workers back into jobs.
