OL,7,FWith 15% of disabled people reporting
OL,8,Fworkplace discrimination relating to
OL,9,Ftheir disability in 2022, the report
OL,10,Fsaid this remains a "pressing issue".
OL,12,FThe think tank said: "Boosting
OL,13,Fdisability employment is not
OL,14,Fstraightforward: it will involve
OL,15,Fimprovements to the health system,
OL,16,Fbenefits system and world of work. But
OL,17,Faction to incentivise and support
OL,18,Femployers is a vital piece of the
OL,19,Fpuzzle."
