OL,7,FLouise Murphy, senior economist at the
OL,8,FResolution Foundation, said: "The
OL,9,FGovernment should do more to
OL,10,Fincentivise firms to employ disabled
OL,11,Fpeople ` especially those who have
OL,12,Fbeen out of work for long periods `
OL,13,Fbut employers need to do more in
OL,14,Freturn.
OL,16,F"A new right to reintegration could
OL,17,Fhelp disabled workers back into work
OL,18,Fin the same way that maternity rights
OL,19,Ftransformed women's employment
OL,20,Fprospects a generation ago."
